      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  INIT   - Subroutine to do Program Initialisation.            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: Main Processing                                   *
      *  Calls:                                                       *
      *  AOBANKR0 Access Program                                      *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           INIT      BEGSR                           ***  INIT  ***
      *
      ** Set up copyright parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
      ***  Receive Parameter List.
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C*********************PARM           OPT     10                      CSC007
     C                     PARM           OPT     1                       CSC007
     C                     PARM           SEQNO   5
      *
      ***  Initialise indicators which condition printer file output.
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C***********OPT*******WHEQ*1****************                         CSC007
     C           OPT       WHEQ '1'                                       CSC007
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN51
     C***********OPT*******WHEQ*2****************                         CSC007
     C           OPT       WHEQ '2'                                       CSC007
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN52
     C***********OPT*******WHEQ*3****************                         CSC007
     C           OPT       WHEQ '3'                                       CSC007
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN53
     C                     ENDSL
